                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-187-off1011 t18220220-187-cd1012"></join>, one watch, value 4 l.; one ribbon, value 2 d.; one seal, value 3 s.; two keys, value 2 d., and one compass, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     
